metadata.name: Botan & Chou
metadata.description: The patterns of "Botan & Chou" are traditional patterns of the "Chinen Bingata" of the Chinen family, one of the three Bingata families that flourished during the Ryukyu Dynasty. It is one of the representative patterns of Ryukyu Bingata, which expresses the rich nature and characteristics of Okinawa with vivid colors and patterns.
